#X text 25 120 Kique v2 — kick drum synth (Faust export);
#X text 25 145 Controls (0-1):;
#X text 25 165 trig — momentanous bang to trigger;
#X text 25 185 f base — base pitch (0=40Hz, 1=160Hz);
#X text 25 205 X — saturation (drive the tanh chain);
#X text 25 225 decay — click/sub decay envelope;
#X text 25 245 famt — pitch envelope amount;
#X text 25 265 namt — noise amount (high-passed);
#X text 25 285 fold — wavefolding amount;
#X text 25 305 decay2 — secondary (sub) decay;
#X text 25 325 delay — sub delay before secondary envelope;
#X text 25 360 Connect a [metro] + [bang] to the left inlet, or;
#X text 25 380 use [trigger] and a message like [; Kique_v2~ trig 1(;
